data.description: Nestled on a spacious lot, this remarkable property offers a unique blend of comfort and versatility. The master bedroom is strategically separated from other bedrooms, ensuring a peaceful retreat. The two-story building and shipping container are insulated for year-round comfort, with the two-story structure featuring two HVAC units.A 30'X25' two-story steel building with a roll-up door and a 26'X17' steel awning takes center stage. This versatile space awaits your creative touch. A 40'X8' conex with power is set up as a workshop. Outdoor amenities include a 30'X23' covered patio with power and water, a 28'X15' pergola, and a 14'X11' cinder block tack room. The property also boasts a 50'X13' steel-framed chicken coop with nesting area and feed storage. An underground handgun range adds a unique touch. Don't miss this opportunity! RNDC offers a Down Payment Assistance Program for First-Time Home Buyers, providing up to $25,000. Call now to make this unique property your forever home!
